REQUIREMENTS TO BUILD:
======================

OCaml 3.12 or newer.

Menhir:
Ubuntu/Debian: libmenhir-ocaml-dev
Fedora: ocaml-menhir-devel

PCRE bindings for OCaml
Ubuntu/Devian: libpcre-ocaml-dev
Fedora: ocaml-pcre-devel

Ulex unicode tokenizer
Ubuntu/Debian: ocaml-ulex
Fedora: ocaml-ulex-devel

Also required for Fedora:
ocaml-camlp4-devel, ocaml-findlib-devel

